# Netflix's Simian Army: a catalog of failure modes
direction: down

Title: "NETFLIX SIMIAN ARMY (the OG chaos toolkit)\nEach 'monkey' simulates a specific real-world failure mode." {
  style: { fill: "#fff4c2"; stroke: "#bf360c"; stroke-width: 2; border-radius: 10 }
}

Chaos: "CHAOS MONKEY\nrandomly terminates instances\n\u2192 verifies graceful instance loss" {
  style: { fill: "#ffcdd2"; stroke: "#b71c1c"; stroke-width: 2; border-radius: 8 }
}

Gorilla: "CHAOS GORILLA\nsimulates entire AZ outage\n\u2192 verifies multi-AZ failover" {
  style: { fill: "#ffcdd2"; stroke: "#b71c1c"; stroke-width: 2; border-radius: 8 }
}

Kong: "CHAOS KONG\nsimulates entire REGION outage\n\u2192 verifies multi-region failover" {
  style: { fill: "#ffcdd2"; stroke: "#b71c1c"; stroke-width: 2; border-radius: 8 }
}

Latency: "LATENCY MONKEY\ninjects artificial latency\n\u2192 verifies timeout / circuit-breaker handling" {
  style: { fill: "#fff59d"; stroke: "#bf360c"; stroke-width: 2; border-radius: 8 }
}

ConformityM: "CONFORMITY MONKEY\nfinds non-conforming instances\n(missing tags, security groups, autoscaling, etc.)\n\u2192 enforces ops standards" {
  style: { fill: "#bbdefb"; stroke: "#0d47a1"; stroke-width: 2; border-radius: 8 }
}

Doctor: "DOCTOR MONKEY\nperforms health checks\nreports unhealthy instances\n\u2192 keeps fleet healthy" {
  style: { fill: "#a5d6a7"; stroke: "#1b5e20"; stroke-width: 2; border-radius: 8 }
}

Janitor: "JANITOR MONKEY\nfinds and cleans unused resources\n\u2192 cost / cleanliness" {
  style: { fill: "#a5d6a7"; stroke: "#1b5e20"; stroke-width: 2; border-radius: 8 }
}

Security: "SECURITY MONKEY\nfinds security misconfigurations\n(open S3 buckets, expired certs, etc.)\n\u2192 enforces security baseline" {
  style: { fill: "#e1bee7"; stroke: "#4a148c"; stroke-width: 2; border-radius: 8 }
}

Spread: "BEYOND NETFLIX: every major cloud / SRE org now does some form of this:\nGoogle DiRT (Disaster Recovery Testing), AWS Fault Injection Service,\nAzure Chaos Studio, GCP Chaos Toolkit, LinkedIn Waterbear, Gremlin (vendor),\nLitmus (CNCF), Chaos Mesh (CNCF), Pumba (Docker chaos), Toxiproxy (network)" {
  style: { fill: "#fff59d"; stroke: "#bf360c"; border-radius: 8 }
}

Title -> Chaos; Title -> Gorilla; Title -> Kong; Title -> Latency
Title -> ConformityM; Title -> Doctor; Title -> Janitor; Title -> Security
Chaos -> Spread
Kong -> Spread
Security -> Spread
